## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

###
## ─── Camping (anywhere, time-based regen) ───
###

### Start camping (auto-duration — recovers until full or 10 min max)
POST {{host}}/rest/camp
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

### Start camping with custom duration (60 seconds)
POST {{host}}/rest/camp
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "duration": 60
}

### Start camping with short duration (30 seconds)
POST {{host}}/rest/camp
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "duration": 30
}

###
## ─── Rest Status ───
###

### Check rest progress
GET {{host}}/rest/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Stop Resting ───
###

### Stop resting early (partial recovery)
POST {{host}}/rest/stop
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Inn (instant full restore, town only) ───
###

### Rest at an inn (must be at a town)
POST {{host}}/rest/inn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Error Cases ───
###

### Try to camp when already at full HP/mana — should fail
POST {{host}}/rest/camp
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

### Try to rest at inn when not at a town — should fail
POST {{host}}/rest/inn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Try to travel while resting — should fail (409 Conflict)
POST {{host}}/travel/move
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "direction": "north"
}

### Try to cast a spell while resting — should fail (409 Conflict)
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "heal"
}

### Try to stop resting when not resting — should fail
POST {{host}}/rest/stop
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
